commit 262b36dbdcd998e07a1497b0e99f1196dd7a2f59
Author: Chris Marshall <marshallch@users.sourceforge.net>
Date:   Wed Jul 15 20:11:19 2009 -0400

    Minor tweakws to .gitignore and MANIFEST.SKIP

